A CRAN-style repository (that's what you want) looks like this:

some_root/-
           |
           - src/contrib/
           |             |
           |             - PACKAGES 
           |             |
           |             - *.tar.gz packages here
           |
           - bin/
                 |
                 - windows/contrib/2.3/
                 |                     |
                 |                     - PACKAGES
                 |                     |
                 |                     - *.zip packages here
                 |
                 - macosx/ppc/contrib/2.3/
                                          |
                                          - PACKAGES
                                          |
                                          - *.tgz packages here



